  EffectDiscription_ENG: "Digivolve: 4 from Lv.5 w/[Etemon] or [Sukamon] in name[All
    Turns][Once Per Turn] When another Digimon with [Etemon] or [Sukamon] in its
    name is deleted, 1 of your opponent's Digimon gets -3000 DP and gains \uFF1CSecurity
